# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================
#
# This .gitignore is specifically designed for the Football Pool Domination System.
# It balances security (ignoring sensitive data) with development convenience.
#
# Key principles:
# 1. Never commit API keys or sensitive data
# 2. Ignore generated/cache files that can be recreated
# 3. Ignore user-specific IDE files
# 4. Ignore temporary and log files
# 5. Keep example files but ignore actual data files
#
# If you need to commit example data, rename files to *_template.json
# =============================================================================
